    #                                                                          #
    ############################################################################
    
    
    
    ****************************************************************************
    **********************         Click 'Run' Now        **********************
    ****************************************************************************
    
    ** This line marks the end of the user-defined inputs and variables. **
    
    What follows is the bulk of the script for module 1 - below this line 
    the user does not need to further change anything. Comments are 
